items.title: Protesters heckle Vance, Hegseth at photo op to thank National Guard troops in DC
items.description: Vice President JD Vance was met with protester boos during a photo op with National Guard troops at Union Station.

items.title: Hurricane Erin live updates: Conditions across Outer Banks to deteriorate soon
items.description: Hurricane Erin has triggered a state of emergency in North Carolina, where residents and visitors along the Outer Banks are under evacuation orders.

items.title: Judge denies DOJ's request to unseal Epstein grand jury records
items.description: A federal judge in New York has denied the Department of Justice's request to unseal grand jury material from Jeffrey Epstein's criminal case.

items.description: CEO Julie Felss Masino dishes on fan feedback, while Robin Roberts asks the question on all of our minds.
